OL,3,CRetail workers face 'shocking' abuse
OL,4,Cas shoplifting cases double
OL,6,FRetail workers are falling victim to
OL,7,Fviolence and abuse, as shoplifting
OL,8,Fcases "double" in Wales.
OL,10,FShop owners have expressed concern of
OL,11,Fthe rising incidents, with the Welsh
OL,12,FRetail Consortium calling for tougher
OL,13,Fpenalties for those who break the law.
OL,15,FMatthew Hunt, director of Filco
OL,16,FSupermarkets in Llantwit Major, said
OL,17,Fthere was a huge spike in shoplifting
OL,18,Factivity in the stores last year and
OL,19,Fnow the company has switched to AI
OL,20,Fprogrammes and CCTV monitoring.
