OL,3,CRetail workers face 'shocking' abuse
OL,4,Cas shoplifting cases double
OL,6,FHe said: "Towards the end of last year
OL,7,Ffrom about August to October, we saw a
OL,8,Fhuge spike in (shoplifting) activity
OL,9,Fin the stores and we were looking at
OL,10,Fgang style team of people entering the
OL,11,Fstore specifically targeting products
OL,12,Fthat they needed."
OL,14,FHe added: "We saw that activity spike
OL,15,Fthrough the back end of last year. We
OL,16,Ftook the decision at that point to
OL,17,Fincrease our protection.
