OL,3,CRetail workers face 'shocking' abuse
OL,4,Cas shoplifting cases double
OL,6,F"There are three layers of protection
OL,7,Fin the store. We use CCTV monitoring.
OL,8,FWe've got AI programme that monitors
OL,9,Fsuspicious behaviour.
OL,11,F"So, individuals putting things in
OL,12,Ftheir pockets or bags, that would be
OL,13,Fhighlighted to us. And we also deploy
OL,14,Ffacial recognition for those people
OL,15,Fwho have been prosecuted of a theft in
OL,16,Four stores.
OL,18,F"They'll get loaded onto the programme
OL,19,Fand we'll get a notification when they
OL,20,Fenter the store."
