OL,3,CRetail workers face 'shocking' abuse
OL,4,Cas shoplifting cases double
OL,6,FThe latest ONS available data for the
OL,7,Fyear ending June 2023 shows there were
OL,8,F19,353 recorded offences of
OL,9,Fshoplifting in Wales between July 2022
OL,10,Fand June 2023.
OL,12,FSara Jones, director of the Welsh
OL,13,FRetail Consortium called figures of
OL,14,Fviolence towards shop workers is
OL,15,F"truly horrendous".
OL,17,FShe said: "I think we are really
OL,18,Fshocked by the figures of violence and
OL,19,Fabuse towards shop workers.
