OL,3,CRetail workers face 'shocking' abuse
OL,4,Cas shoplifting cases double
OL,6,F"What we've seen is a doubling in the
OL,7,Fnumber of those incidents and it's
OL,8,Fsomething that I know our retailers
OL,9,Fspend a huge amount of money in terms
OL,10,Fof trying to support and keep
OL,11,Fcolleagues safe.
OL,13,F"But what we need to see is a similar
OL,14,Fresponse both from the police but also
OL,15,Ffrom the UK government and we're
OL,16,Fasking from them to create a stand
OL,17,Falone offence of violence and abuse
OL,18,Ftowards retail staff."
