OL,6,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "The
OL,7,Fpolicing minister has been clear
OL,8,Fpolice must take a zero-tolerance
OL,9,Fapproach to shoplifting. Violence
OL,10,Fagainst a retail worker is
OL,11,Funacceptable, which is why we made it
OL,12,Fan aggravating offence to ensure
OL,13,Ftougher sentences for perpetrators.
OL,15,F"We continue to work closely with
OL,16,Fretailers. The police have committed
OL,17,Fto patrol more areas and attend more
OL,18,Fshoplifting incidents, especially
OL,19,Fwhere violence has occurred.
