OL,6,F"Good progress has been made on these
OL,7,Fcommitments, however we will continue
OL,8,Fworking closely with police and the
OL,9,Fsector to catch more perpetrators."
OL,11,FChief inspector Dan Howe said: "The
OL,12,FRetail Crime Action Plan, launched in
OL,13,FOctober last year, sets out our
OL,14,Fcommitment to tackling shoplifting and
OL,15,Fprioritising attendance where violence
OL,16,Fwas involved or a shoplifter was
OL,17,Fdetained.
