OL,4,Cas shoplifting cases double
OL,6,F"In the first month after the Plan was
OL,7,Flaunched there were positive outcome
OL,8,Ffor 287 crimes in Cardiff including
OL,9,Fcharges and cautions. 254 of these
OL,10,Fhave been in the city centre.
OL,12,F"This is more than double the volume
OL,13,Fof the same period last year so
OL,14,Fdemonstrates the impact that we're
OL,15,Fhaving but also underlines the scale
OL,16,Fof the issue and importance of
OL,17,Fembedding the benefits over the longer
OL,18,Fterm.
