OL,6,F"In addition to these charges, many of
OL,7,Fthe offenders have been linked to
OL,8,Fcrimes that were previously reported
OL,9,Fand admitted their involvement.
OL,11,F"As such, several of the more prolific
OL,12,Foffenders will appear in court with
OL,13,Fthese matters being taken into
OL,14,Fconsideration, which will feature as
OL,15,Fpart of the sentencing decision.
OL,16,FOperational implementation of the plan
OL,17,Fhas shown significant impact in terms
OL,18,Fof police attendance to this type of
OL,19,Fincident.
