OL,6,F"A number of factors impact police
OL,7,Fattendance and includes whether an
OL,8,Foffender has left the scene or been
OL,9,Flet go before police were called, how
OL,10,Fsoon after the incident it is
OL,11,Freported, whether a retailer may not
OL,12,Fsupport a prosecution, or when
OL,13,Fofficers are dealing with or are
OL,14,Fdiverted to an urgent incident
OL,15,Felsewhere.
