OL,4,Cas shoplifting cases double
OL,6,F"We know retail crime can have a
OL,7,Fsignificant impact on victims, which
OL,8,Fis why we are committed to doing all
OL,9,Fwe can to reduce thefts and pursue
OL,10,Foffenders, especially those prolific
OL,11,Fand habitual offenders who cause
OL,12,Fmisery within the community.
OL,14,F"The Retail Crime Action Plan sets out
OL,15,Fclear guidelines for the response to
OL,16,Fretail crime this has been embedded
OL,17,Finto our operational work.
